---
title: Savoury Beef and Mushroom Pasta with Green Peas and Spinach
description: Leaning on inspiration from 'Salisbury steak',  this unctuous beef and mushroom pasta with sweet peas and baby spinach is ready in 15 minutes or less!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/savoury-beef-and-mushroom-pasta-d8f2a50b-cf22616f.jpg
